{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Server-sent events","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>網頁一般來說是由客戶端向伺服器請求資料. 藉由 server-sent 事件, 伺服器在任何時候都可以向客戶端推送資料. 即將推送進來的訊息可以自客戶端上做 <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Events (en-US)</a> + data</em> 處理.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"文件","title":"文件","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"使用\">使用 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events/Using_server-sent_events\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">server-sent events (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>有關如何在伺服器端和客戶端使用 server-sent 事件的教學文章.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"參考\">參考 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">EventSource (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>關於客戶端的 EventSource API.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"工具","title":"工具","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>Remy Sharp’s <a href=\"https://github.com/remy/polyfills/blob/master/EventSource.js\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">EventSource polyfill</a></li>\n  <li>Yaffle’s <a href=\"https://github.com/Yaffle/EventSource\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">EventSource polyfill</a></li>\n  <li>Rick Waldron’s <a href=\"https://github.com/rwldrn/jquery.eventsource\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">jquery plugin</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相關主題","title":"相關主題","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Guide/AJAX\">AJAX</a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API\">WebSockets</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecifica